search_results.title: Aly Colón
search_results.snippet: Aly Colón is the Knight Professor of Media Ethics in the Department of Journalism and Mass Communications at Washington and Lee University.

search_results.title: Bachtiar Aly
search_results.snippet: Bachtiar Aly is a professor from Indonesia who majored in Communication and Politics. He was the Indonesian Ambassador for Egypt from 2002–2005.
